cosmos-adminlinks-edit-css: Text for 'Edit CSS file' in Special:AdminLinks, when the AdminLinks extension is installed.
cosmos-adminlinks-edit-js: Text for 'Edit JS file' in Special:AdminLinks, when the AdminLinks extension is installed.
cosmos-adminlinks-edit-navigation: Text for 'Edit navigation' in Special:AdminLinks, when the AdminLinks extension is installed.
cosmos-adminlinks-edit-tagline: Text for 'Edit tagline' in Special:AdminLinks, when the AdminLinks extension is installed.
cosmos-anonymous:
The text that shows instead of a username in the top banner if the user is not logged in.

{{Identical|Anonymous}}
cosmos-counter-label: The label for the article counter in wiki navigation. Uses Plural:$1.
cosmos-createpage-header: The header for the create page pop-up dialog.
cosmos-createpage-input-label: The new page's name input label.
cosmos-createpage-next: The create page dialog submit/next button label.
cosmos-createpage-wanted-pages: The second part of cosmos-createpage-text if the wanted pages feature is enabled.
cosmos-createpage-no-wanted-pages: The second part of cosmos-createpage-text if the wanted pages feature is not enabled.
cosmos-personaltools-userpage:
The link text for user page in personal tools.

{{Identical|User page}}
cosmos-personaltools-usertalk: The link text for a logged in user's talk page in personal tools.
cosmos-personaltools-anontalk: The link text for an anonymous user's talk page in personal tools.
cosmos-editcount-label: The label for the edit count displayed on social profile user pages.
cosmos-action-addsection:
The new topic link text displayed on talk pages.

{{Identical|New topic}}
cosmos-action-cancel:
The label for the action cancel buttons.

{{Identical|Cancel}}
cosmos-action-backtopage: The label for the 'Back to $1' button, when the $1 is relevant.
cosmos-action-back:
The label of the back button.

{{Identical|Back}}
cosmos-add-new-image: The Add New Image text used in the header.
cosmos-add-new-video: The Add New Video text used in the header.
cosmos-add-new-page-title: The html title attribute for the add new page button.
cosmos-add-new-page-text:
The label for the add page button if user is logged in.

{{Identical|Add}}
cosmos-anon-add-new-page-text: The label for the add new page button if the user is not logged in.
cosmos-explore:
The header for the explore tab in the navigation.

{{Identical|Explore}}
cosmos-user-blocked:
The text used to show a user is blocked on social profile Pages' avatar area.

{{Identical|Blocked}}
cosmos-search-loader: Text to display below search input while the search suggestion module is loading
cosmos-searchsuggest-containing: Label used in the special item of the search suggestions list which gives the user an option to perform a full text search for the term. Used in the Codex typeahead search component.
cosmos-article-header-categories-in: Label displayed before list of categories that given article belongs to
cosmos-article-header-categories-more: Link to more categories that are hidden by default
cosmos-themedesigner-success: Message displayed when the theme designer form is submitted.
cosmos-themedesigner-text: Header text for the ThemeDesigner special page.
themedesigner: Display name of the ThemeDesigner special page.
